newsitem.title: USA: U.S. corn gluten feed and meal prices unchanged.
newsitem.headline: U.S. corn gluten feed and meal prices unchanged.

text.p: U.S. corn gluten feed and meal prices were unchanged on Thursday amid slow movement, dealers said. One Illinois mill stopped selling meal temporarily due to production cutbacks for maintenance.
